<h1><i class="fa fa-briefcase"></i>Workplace Collaboration</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-home"></i>Home</a></li>
	<li><a href="#uses"><i class="fa fa-user-circle"></i>Uses</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-users"></i>Workplace Collaboration</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<div class="attention"><i class="fa fa-briefcase"></i></div>

	<div class="description section">
		<p>The workplace collaboration features make it easy for you to communicate with your co-workers, whether in the same office or distributed around the world.  You can exchange messages, news, files, documents, folders, images, code, music, or whatever you're working on together! </p>
	</div>

	<div class="details section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-exchange-alt"></i>An Alternative To</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Slack</li>
					<li>Microsoft Teams</li>
					<li>Google Hangouts</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-star"></i>Benefits</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Exchange direct messages with colleagues. </li>
					<li>Post news and announcements. </li>
					<li>Exchange files and folders in addition to your messages and news posts. </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2><i class="fa fa-desktop"></i>Screen Shots</h2>
	<div class="figure desktop-only">
		<a href="images/info/apps/communicator/communicator.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="<%= config.apps['communicator'].name %>"><img class="dialog" src="images/info/apps/communicator/communicator.png" /></a>
		<div class="caption"><%= config.apps['communicator'].name %></div>
	</div>
	<div class="figure desktop-only">
		<a href="images/info/apps/chat-viewer/chat-viewer.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="<%= config.apps['chat_viewer'].name %>"><img class="dialog" src="images/info/apps/chat-viewer/chat-viewer.png" /></a>
		<div class="caption"><%= config.apps['chat_viewer'].name %></div>
	</div>
	<div class="figure row mobile-only">
		<div class="figure col-sm-6">
			<a href="images/info/apps/communicator/mobile/mobile-communicator.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="<%= config.apps['communicator'].name %>"><img class="dialog" src="images/info/apps/communicator/mobile/mobile-communicator.png" /></a>
			<div class="caption"><%= config.apps['communicator'].name %></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>